public class MotorsView
extends uk.co.dancowan.robots.ui.views.ScrolledView

Eclipse View implementation exposes motor drive commands in several aspects.

Command pad also exposes a number of configurable function keys which can be used with atomic commands from the AtomicCommandFactory class.
